### LabVerse Android App - Team API Test Suite
### Base URL: http://10.0.2.2:8081/api/teams
### Note: 10.0.2.2 is the Android emulator's alias for localhost

@baseUrl = http://10.0.2.2:8081/api/teams
@contentType = application/json

### Variables
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@teamId = YOUR_TEAM_ID_HERE
@userId = YOUR_USER_ID_HERE
@memberId = YOUR_MEMBER_ID_HERE

### 1. Create Team
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "AI Research Lab",
  "description": "Research team focused on artificial intelligence",
  "researchField": "Artificial Intelligence",
  "privacy": "PRIVATE",
  "iconUrl": "https://example.com/icon.png"
}

### 2. Get Team by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{teamId}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 3. List Teams (with filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}?search=AI&researchField=Artificial%20Intelligence&privacy=PUBLIC&page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 4. List Teams (no filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}?page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 5. Update Team
PUT {{baseUrl}}/{{teamId}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Updated Team Name",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "researchField": "Machine Learning",
  "privacy": "PUBLIC",
  "iconUrl": "https://example.com/new-icon.png"
}

### 6. Delete Team
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{teamId}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 7. Add Team Member
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{teamId}}/members
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "role": "RESEARCHER"
}

### 8. Get Team Members
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{teamId}}/members
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 9. Remove Team Member
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{teamId}}/members/{{memberId}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

